WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:22.232
Subtitles and audio translation will begin later. Please wait for the official start of the video.

00:00:22.233 --> 00:00:29.839
Well, good evening family. Praise the Lord. Thank you for joining us again tonight on this Sunday.

00:00:29.840 --> 00:00:34.255
What a wonderful day it's been. You know, the weather's been really pretty in the state of Oklahoma.

00:00:34.256 --> 00:00:41.514
We're believing for more rain. We need a lot more rain. I don't know where you are, but I bet you need rain, too.

00:00:41.515 --> 00:00:49.382
And so, we're going to continue to pray for the rain over this nation. I know there's a lot of people that are in drought.

00:00:49.383 --> 00:00:57.048
And so, before we get into the summer, we only have just a couple more weeks and we'll be into the hot months.

00:00:57.049 --> 00:01:02.977
So, we really need to fill up our lakes and our streams. And Colorado needs rain desperately.

00:01:02.977 --> 00:01:07.446
And so, we're going to call it in. We're going to believe God.

00:01:07.447 --> 00:01:11.740
And that's what we always do. We're going to believe God and we're going to get some rain.

00:01:11.741 --> 00:01:22.136
You know, I just thought about all the things that the Lord has done this week and just being thankful for every single thing that he has done, giving him holy praise.

00:01:22.137 --> 00:01:30.769
Like Paul and Silas in the midnight hour giving him praise in the prison and the walls began to shake.

00:01:30.770 --> 00:01:38.414
They weren't praying, they were praising. And in the praise, God delivered them out of the prison.

00:01:38.415 --> 00:01:43.166
And I think tonight's a good night for whatever you've been through this week.

00:01:43.167 --> 00:01:49.763
The walls will begin to shake in your life. The walls that have held you back, that have held you captive.

00:01:49.764 --> 00:02:05.759
I feel it in my heart tonight that the Lord is saying, if you just give me some praise where you are, in your circumstance, the walls that have been holding you captive will begin to shake in your life.

00:02:05.760 --> 00:02:11.643
And I know that this is true. I felt it in my spirit as I was praying this afternoon.

00:02:11.644 --> 00:02:18.529
And he said, I've done some good things, Brandon, and a lot of people, I've healed their bodies.

00:02:18.530 --> 00:02:27.905
I've delivered them from some things. And I need some gratitude. Some gratitude.

00:02:27.906 --> 00:02:33.679
Let's just praise him for just a couple minutes for everything he's done in your life.

00:02:33.680 --> 00:02:37.525
You may say, Well, Brandon, I just have just a little bit of a breakthrough.

00:02:37.526 --> 00:02:47.639
Praise him for the breakthrough that you have. Praise him for where you are, that you're not where you used to be.

00:02:47.640 --> 00:02:54.079
And I believe in doing so the manifestation of what you're believing for. There's an expiration date on it.

00:02:54.080 --> 00:02:59.809
And I'm telling you, I believe with all my heart that God is a God that will deliver his people.

00:02:59.810 --> 00:03:07.392
And there's expiration dates to what you've been believing for. All things are possible to him who believes.

00:03:07.393 --> 00:03:12.833
So, Father, we just give you praise and glory and honor for this prayer time tonight.

00:03:12.834 --> 00:03:17.047
We praise you, Father, for the breakthrough, for whatever they're believing for.

00:03:17.048 --> 00:03:27.518
Father, in their health, in their minds and their emotions and their marriages, Father, we thank you, Lord, for the week that we had, and I thank you for the week that we're about to start.

00:03:27.519 --> 00:03:34.465
We're so grateful, Father, that you have showed up and showed off in our lives over the month of April.

00:03:34.466 --> 00:03:43.428
There were so many breakthroughs and so many things that we saw in prayer. And Lord, we thank you for the month of May.

00:03:43.429 --> 00:03:51.672
We start out this month of May, Father, with great expectation for great turnaround in our circumstances.

00:03:51.673 --> 00:04:01.719
No matter what it is that we're believing for, Father, we're believing for exceedingly abundantly above all that we dare ask or think. So, Father, we dedicate this month to you.

00:04:01.720 --> 00:04:14.112
We dedicate the month of May that this will be the beginning of supernatural blessing and increase, healing, marriages restored, children coming home, whatever they may need.

00:04:14.113 --> 00:04:18.543
Father, I thank you, Lord, that we praise you in that midnight hour.

00:04:18.544 --> 00:04:23.499
And I believe the walls of our circumstances are shaking right now.

00:04:23.500 --> 00:04:28.475
They're shaking. And I thank you, Lord, that Father, the chains have been broken.

00:04:28.476 --> 00:04:43.772
You were crucified for us and Father you were resurrected on the third day and you dwell in us in the name of Jesus richly by faith and we believe that Father the breakthrough of what we're believing for is right at hand.

00:04:43.772 --> 00:04:57.674
Jobs and better jobs, raises and bonuses, benefits, sales and commissions, growth in businesses and states and inheritances, rebates and returns, checks in the mail, gifts and surprises.

00:04:57.675 --> 00:05:06.354
Do you believe that? Finding money, bills paid off, blessing and increase, healing in your body, from the top of your head to the soles of your feet.

00:05:06.355 --> 00:05:10.476
I believe that God is a rewarder of those that diligently seek him.

00:05:10.477 --> 00:05:13.985
And Father, we thank you, Lord, that you're the healer and you're the deliverer.

00:05:13.986 --> 00:05:22.959
And Father, we thank you for the good things that we're about to see in the rest of this year, 2026.

00:05:22.960 --> 00:05:41.559
We are ahead of schedule. 2026. Wow. Where have I been? Interesting.

00:05:41.560 --> 00:05:57.039
When I was seeing it over in the spirit realm. There was things I was seeing over just not even an hour ago.

00:05:57.040 --> 00:06:04.399
And it was concerning the years and what the Lord is showing me.

00:06:04.400 --> 00:06:19.079
2026, 2027. Where are we at in 2027? What does 2027 look like? But what does the rest of 2026 look like?

00:06:19.080 --> 00:06:29.679
And as I was looking over into it, as I was praying, he said, I have some things I need to show you before you start your live stream.

00:06:29.680 --> 00:06:46.319
And the shaking of our nation, the shaking of the nations. We've never been in a time like we're about to see.

00:06:46.320 --> 00:07:07.359
When the Lord said in 2025, that's what he said on September the 23rd, you would enter into the point of no return, the point of acceleration whenever they had the UN meeting and it was all about Israel and the things that were taking place and then we entered into this year.

00:07:07.360 --> 00:07:13.209
But I'm trying to warn you. We're about to enter in a time like we've never seen before.

00:07:13.210 --> 00:07:21.239
Even more with all the wars and the rumors of wars, an acceleration above everything we've ever seen before.

00:07:21.240 --> 00:07:28.479
And I'm telling you by the spirit of God, we're about to see signs and wonders in these last days like we've never seen before.

00:07:28.480 --> 00:07:32.759
Oh, I don't believe that. Well, that's okay. You don't have to experience it.

00:07:32.760 --> 00:07:45.279
I believe with all my heart that we're about to see God show up and show off in our lives and demonstrations and manifestations of the glory.

00:07:45.280 --> 00:07:57.079
And I have expectation for what God is about to do in the latter part of this year going into 2027.

00:07:57.080 --> 00:08:19.918
As I was looking to the east, you know, whenever you see things and he talks about martyrs and he was talking to me about martyrs in the body of Christ and he was saying that there's a lot of people he said there'll be a lot of martyrs in the days ahead.

00:08:19.919 --> 00:08:30.159
I said I don't really like that. He said, Well, Brandon, there will be a lot of martyrs in the days ahead.

00:08:30.160 --> 00:08:37.079
I saw certain people that I'm familiar with on stages preaching and they just went home.

00:08:37.080 --> 00:08:41.516
I watched them as they were preaching the gospel and they were taken out by sniper.

00:08:41.517 --> 00:08:47.520
Couldn't figure out why the covering wasn't there. I was praying over these things.

00:08:47.521 --> 00:08:53.999
I said, So, are you asking me to change this? What are you at? What is this?

00:08:54.000 --> 00:09:02.879
Why are you showing me this? And he said, Some people will come home.

00:09:02.880 --> 00:09:12.599
He talked about sovereignty today. He talked a lot about things that are very hard for me to talk about.

00:09:12.600 --> 00:09:19.563
And he said, My sovereign hand will move the people. I saw the people moving.

00:09:19.564 --> 00:09:29.719
I saw great migration again. I saw this nation shaking. I saw things that were frightening to me a little bit in the natural.

00:09:29.720 --> 00:09:34.359
And as I got fearful, he yelled three times, Fear not, Brandon.

00:09:34.360 --> 00:09:47.759
Fear not. Fear not for what you're looking at, for what's coming. Keep your eyes on me. I will hide you in the cliff of the rock.

00:09:47.760 --> 00:09:58.759
1 Corinthians 5:5 will start to come to full manifestation, a shaking and an awakening of the bride to bring her to my side.

00:09:58.760 --> 00:10:12.079
For there is a slumber upon the nations. There is, they're asleep and there will be an awakening unto God.

00:10:12.080 --> 00:10:20.811
Awakening unto God for what is about to take place. And it will be around the world for the bride is asleep.

00:10:20.812 --> 00:10:32.039
A lot of them. And this is one last call, for the sun is setting on this dispensation of grace. The sun is setting.

00:10:32.040 --> 00:10:43.934
And as I saw a building exploding—it looked like some kind of device, a nuclear device or something in a building up northeast—it was a major building.

00:10:43.935 --> 00:10:49.823
And I saw it; I saw this device going off up northeast. It looked like nuclear.

00:10:49.824 --> 00:10:54.848
Something happens. I saw something very, very tragic taking place.

00:10:54.849 --> 00:11:04.279
And then I saw the headlines in the papers, and I saw, 'Terror strikes again.

00:11:04.280 --> 00:11:24.359
Terror strikes again.'And then I saw in the headlines, 'Terror in the heartland.'A nation in turmoil.

00:11:24.360 --> 00:11:35.839
I saw this in the headlines in black bold letters: 'Nation in Turmoil.'I wasn't going to jump right into this, but I don't want to waste your time.

00:11:35.840 --> 00:11:44.791
I have such an urgency in my heart to tell you: you must wake up. I see the headlines in the papers.

00:11:44.792 --> 00:11:52.705
I see what the Lord is showing me concerning this nation and other nations—a shaking to awaken.

00:11:52.706 --> 00:12:01.776
As I told you, Cuba is next. The Lord said Cuba is next. He's going to liberate the people.

00:12:01.777 --> 00:12:09.159
A major revival is coming to Cuba. A major outpouring of the Spirit of God is coming to Cuba.

00:12:09.160 --> 00:12:20.719
And God is going to use Marco Rubio in the days ahead to bring—it was personal to him.

00:12:20.720 --> 00:12:36.838
And I saw him in the hand of the Lord being led; and David slew his tens of thousands and Saul slew his thousands.

00:12:36.839 --> 00:12:42.359
There are things that you will see Marco Rubio do in the days ahead.

00:12:42.360 --> 00:12:59.350
And a shaking to Cuba and to the Latino community—it's going to be epic—a huge move of God in the Latino community and in the Asian community.

00:12:59.351 --> 00:13:09.159
I'm not just singling them out, but this is what I have been praying over this weekend.

00:13:09.160 --> 00:13:18.999
And I want to show you what President Trump just said that goes with everything that we've been praying, to show you we're on target with our prayers.

00:13:19.000 --> 00:13:39.319
And President Trump came out publicly and he said this: 'An architect who's really talented—he's done a lot of work for him—he's got a flair, a beautiful Hispanic flair in particular.

00:13:39.320 --> 00:13:56.119
And he comes from originally a place called Cuba, which we will be taking over almost immediately.'No, Cuba's got problems. We'll finish one first; I like to finish a job.

00:13:56.120 --> 00:14:13.079
On the way back from what we'll do on the way back from Iran, we'll have one of our big, maybe the USS Abraham Lincoln aircraft carrier, the biggest in the world—we'll have that come in, stop about a hundred yards offshore, and they'll say, "Thank you very much.

00:14:13.080 --> 00:14:27.677
We give up."Good job. It's coming. The Lord said it's coming and the shaking of Cuba is coming. I truly believe this with all my heart.

00:14:27.678 --> 00:14:39.159
The Lord said, 'I'm going to bring great revival to Cuba.'And he's joking about it, but I believe he's really serious in his heart.

00:14:39.160 --> 00:14:45.239
Then the Lord showed us a major thing about to take place with Ukraine.

00:14:45.240 --> 00:14:52.079
And I saw Zelensky. He was doing cocaine and he had prostitutes around him.

00:14:52.080 --> 00:14:59.919
He had all kinds of things going on in this room. And he was no longer here.

00:14:59.920 --> 00:15:05.919
In the days ahead, I saw him trying to either... and it was two paths.

00:15:05.920 --> 00:15:10.190
I saw him getting on a plane with lots of $100 bills and he was going to another nation.

00:15:10.191 --> 00:15:29.359
And then I've seen him being taken out in this building, and I saw a new government coming in in the days ahead that will be brought in by a proxy government, pro-Ukraine, pro-Russia.

00:15:29.360 --> 00:15:56.399
But I saw Macron in the last vision and the last time I was with you all two days ago, I saw a cardinal striking a dove and the dove was dead upon the ground and his heart was ripped out, and I saw two black crows looking at the dead dove's body.

00:15:56.400 --> 00:16:05.959
I saw a turtle; I saw it had glasses on. I could see the cardinal and the turtle were friends.

00:16:05.960 --> 00:16:27.199
I could see across a weasel. A weasel was in France. I saw a weasel scheming. I could see a cobra coming up out of the Middle East.

00:16:27.200 --> 00:16:44.439
But as I looked at the lifeless bird laying on the ground, the bear was poked with missiles coming out of France, giving them to Ukraine, trying to stir up World War III.

00:16:44.440 --> 00:16:59.959
And as I was looking into that this last week, I saw a plan because I saw Trump trying to pull out of NATO and he said in articles that we're pulling out 5,000 troops out of Germany.

00:16:59.960 --> 00:17:09.919
Do you see it? I've seen that. It was important because that's what we saw Thursday.

00:17:09.920 --> 00:17:28.492
And the Lord warned us that they would try to devise a plan to ensnare the United States in the days ahead to stay in NATO as Trump tries to pull out and says, 'Listen, we're not going to be a part of this anymore because you're not backing us.'And he was asking for help in the Strait.

00:17:28.493 --> 00:17:44.538
And I saw under-the-table deals. Europe rattled by... Do you see it?

00:17:44.539 --> 00:17:48.390
And that's why I saw they would try to provoke it and it manifested.

00:17:48.391 --> 00:17:55.959
This is what we saw on Thursday. And this happened over the next day or so.

00:17:55.960 --> 00:18:03.556
So, I saw a rattling—like what they're saying—but I saw President Trump saying we're going to do this.

00:18:03.557 --> 00:18:08.519
And I saw under-the-table agreements with the king, and he is a scorpion.

00:18:08.520 --> 00:18:26.799
But I saw the chameleon would try to do a coup against President Trump, a coup to overthrow him with the 25th Amendment.

00:18:26.800 --> 00:18:41.279
I saw a coup and the Lord said, 'Don't forget January 6th.'And there were a lot of innocent people that were accused of things and were in there like the pastor out in Amarillo, Brian.

00:18:41.280 --> 00:18:56.079
There are a lot of good people that were accused of things, but you had a bunch of bad apples, deep state in the midst of the January 6th thing that were there to create violence and stir up trouble.

00:18:56.080 --> 00:19:03.061
And the good people were mixed with the bad people. And the Lord said, 'Don't forget January 6th.

00:19:03.062 --> 00:19:11.159
Another event is coming.'There's something else coming to the nation.

00:19:11.160 --> 00:19:33.439
Now, when I'm looking into these visions and the Lord has me praying over them, they're all very similar, yet very different, you know, like the way the picture is and what he's showing me of how to pray for our nation to pray for revival—a shaking in our nation with the buildings burning in New York.

00:19:33.440 --> 00:19:37.871
I see these buildings. I see explosions in the buildings. I see fire.

00:19:37.872 --> 00:20:13.959
And the Lord said, 'Don't forget the prophetic words that I gave to David Wilkerson.'Remember I told you I saw a black, white, and red boat that was an oil tanker that would be hijacked?

00:20:13.960 --> 00:20:22.300
And I said they put a device in the oil and they will hijack the boat.

00:20:22.301 --> 00:20:31.319
And I saw everybody on the crew was murdered and they take the boat and they put a device in it. Does anybody remember that?

00:20:31.320 --> 00:20:48.999
Put in the comment section if you remember a hijacking of a boat when I told you I see a boat that will come out and it will be black, red and white and it will be hijacked and they will put a device in the boat.

00:20:49.000 --> 00:21:03.999
Does anybody remember it? Well, it happened. I don't know where the boat is, but this is interesting to me. Is it the boat that I saw? I don't know.

00:21:04.000 --> 00:21:21.312
All I know is I saw a boat that was red, black, and white, and it was an oil boat, and they put the oil in the middle, and they used a dirty thing in this, and it was a massive device that was dirty, and they would hijack it.

00:21:21.313 --> 00:21:36.719
And I saw all the crew deceased in the boat. I think it was kind of interesting.

00:21:36.720 --> 00:21:52.458
Same colors, everything. But he warned me this was a very dangerous thing. Poland.

00:21:52.459 --> 00:21:59.148
NATO moved a thousand troops with heavy gear to the Russian doorstep in Poland.

00:21:59.149 --> 00:22:05.919
Now, what did I show you? What did I tell you about Poland? Warsaw.

00:22:05.920 --> 00:22:17.220
I said they will provoke Putin in the days ahead and he will use a weapon that has never been used ever before on the face of the earth.

00:22:17.221 --> 00:22:21.536
And it will not disintegrate the buildings or the cars, but it melts the people.

00:22:21.537 --> 00:22:30.796
I've never seen something like that before. But he didn't destroy the land.

00:22:30.797 --> 00:22:42.592
And the Lord said it is not nuclear. It is a weapon that has never been used. It looked like a nuclear weapon, but it wasn't.

00:22:42.593 --> 00:22:53.190
And the Lord said, "This is by Warsaw, Poland."And He said, "They will provoke them in the days ahead."Is this what we're about to see?

00:22:53.191 --> 00:23:05.205
I'm telling you, an acceleration of World War III trying to bring forth the Mahdi. Here it is. Do you see that? I warned you all.

00:23:05.206 --> 00:23:15.799
We've been praying what the Lord showed us, and I saw they would try to keep President Trump from leaving NATO.

00:23:15.800 --> 00:23:25.879
They'll try to snare him. And I saw Emmanuel Macron riding a black swan down the river.

00:23:25.880 --> 00:23:42.599
A massive black swan. And he was riding it down the river in France. Do you see that? Do they see it?

00:23:42.600 --> 00:23:49.919
So, these are the things the Lord has showed us before, and now we see it in the news.

00:23:49.920 --> 00:24:00.235
And I saw a major draft coming out of this. This is what I saw the draft considering. Remember I said why?

00:24:00.236 --> 00:24:09.759
Because Apollyon came up out of the pit and started going like a top, and it looked like a Tasmanian devil.

00:24:09.760 --> 00:24:31.879
Can you show them that? The Tasmanian devil. Okay. I know I'm throwing new things at you, but it's what I'm getting by the spirit of God while I'm talking.

00:24:31.880 --> 00:24:54.879
Keep going. What? It's one of those, baby. I remember. You've done a lot of work, son.

00:24:54.880 --> 00:25:08.856
So we saw a major draft, and that's whenever I saw there was not enough people to fight, and they called for this whenever the major war broke out in Europe. Then North Korea joined it.

00:25:08.857 --> 00:25:31.079
And as I was watching this last vision when we were praying together, I saw China turn its back on Russia and was looking with something in his hand, and he had a smirk on his face as he was looking towards Taiwan, and lights and things were coming out of Taiwan.

00:25:31.080 --> 00:25:42.474
And the Lord said, "Remember this."So, there's things that we're seeing in the news now that are alarming because we're in it.

00:25:42.475 --> 00:26:00.599
Now, go ahead and play this one. This is interesting because this is what I saw in 2023. Talk about it again.

00:26:00.600 --> 00:26:12.345
I saw a demon that was chained in a pit with these massive chains on top of this devil binding him in this pit.

00:26:12.346 --> 00:26:32.711
And I saw an angelic being from the Lord come down and release that demonic spirit, and it came up out of that pit and he started spinning like the Tasmanian devil on Bugs Bunny.

00:26:32.712 --> 00:26:38.986
He was spinning profusely when he got out of that pit, and he went inside Vladimir Putin's area.

00:26:38.987 --> 00:26:53.194
It was like I saw Vladimir Putin—I'm going to say it's like he went inside Vladimir Putin—and all of a sudden I saw him strike Poland because Poland got missiles from other countries.

00:26:53.195 --> 00:27:03.074
Something happened. Poland was provoking Russia because of war stuff and helping out with Ukraine. But there was something more to this.

00:27:03.075 --> 00:27:17.825
So all of a sudden about Warsaw, Poland, I believe is where by the Belarus area, I saw a humongous mushroom cloud kind of an explosion.

00:27:17.826 --> 00:27:34.270
I said, "Lord, oh no, they're going to use tactical nukes."And the Lord said, "No, this is a weapon that has never been used before, ever, on the earth."We've never seen this.

00:27:34.271 --> 00:27:49.029
I saw a demon. That's it. You did good. I like it. That's when you first started.

00:27:49.030 --> 00:28:00.867
But we saw that in prayer, and I saw Warsaw and I saw a provoking of our military to get in this, and that was how many years ago.

00:28:00.868 --> 00:28:07.679
And now we're seeing things on the border. We're seeing President Trump saying, "I'm leaving.

00:28:07.680 --> 00:28:31.399
We're taking our troops out of Germany."And I said, "In this, they will provoke a major war to keep the United States in it because they cannot afford to lose us."And so back then, Biden was in power, and I thought, is Creepy Joe going to do something stupid?

00:28:31.400 --> 00:28:50.712
I didn't see Trump because it was Biden. Well, three years later, we have President Trump back and he's saying, "I'm pulling the troops out of NATO.

00:28:50.713 --> 00:28:59.502
You didn't help me out. I'm going to get my troops out of here."And this is exactly what we saw was a pulling of the troops, a provoking—something's coming.

00:28:59.503 --> 00:29:12.238
And then I saw missiles that look like Tomahawk missiles being given to Ukraine to go deep into Russia from France.

00:29:12.239 --> 00:29:24.179
As I saw the dove on the ground and I saw the heart ripped out, the Lord said, "Don't tell who they are.

00:29:24.180 --> 00:29:41.479
It's not necessary."He says, "It's symbolic by animals for a reason."That's why he gave you doves, cardinals, turtles, because it was code.

00:29:41.480 --> 00:29:48.158
And the Lord said, "I did that on purpose today."I just follow him.

00:29:48.159 --> 00:29:56.679
He said, "I gave it to you in code on purpose."So I gave it to you how he gave it to me.

00:29:56.680 --> 00:30:09.246
I know who the things are and what they represent. You will too if you pray in the spirit.

00:30:09.247 --> 00:30:26.319
Next. He has the cards. He put this on his Truth Social. So he's making a joke. And so he's playing with the cards again.

00:30:26.320 --> 00:30:34.319
I said instead he had the full house in his last hand, now he has all the wilds and he's going to win.

00:30:34.320 --> 00:30:49.060
But the Lord said, "Be humble."Remember, and the Lord said in this, "Do not underestimate your enemy, for they have things that you don't know they have."And maybe you do know they have them now, sir.

00:30:49.061 --> 00:30:56.547
But I saw Cuba and I saw sniffers. Sniffers going all over Cuba trying to sniff it.

00:30:56.548 --> 00:31:04.765
But it was encased in lead. What we were looking for was encased in lead.

00:31:04.766 --> 00:31:14.319
I don't understand what I'm seeing, but I'm just trying to tell you what we are looking for is encased in lead.

00:31:14.320 --> 00:31:25.319
I don't know what that does. All I know is the Lord said, "This is encased in lead, what we're looking for."And they can't smell it.

